'''Tu'snakt''' d tu'ssna yi'mḍanen s-umata, tettwa sileɣ s t'musniwin ti'madwanin (''connaissances abstraites'') s tallat n [[A'zebz|i'zebzan]] [[Tameẓla|i'meẓlan]] (''raisonnements logiques'') ɣef [[ta miḍrant|t'miḍranin]] (''consepts'') am [[amḍan|yi'mḍanen]] (''nombres''), [[ta'nezgit]] (''géométrie''), [[tiskiwt (tusnakt)|ti'skiwin]] (''structures'') neɣ [[i seɣwal i'nezgiyen|i'seɣwal]] (''transformation''). Tu'snakt tbedd daɣen ɣef ta'ɣult n [[ta'gmi tusnit|te'gmi]] (''recherche'') iy ssendalen (''developpe'') ti'musniwin, akk d wayen it sselmad.

== A'ẓuṛ n wa'wal ==

Tu'snakt d a'wal id yussan deg sin wa'walen i'lelliyen '''tu'ssna''' d '''kti''' (tu'ssna= ''science'', ket = ''mesurer''; tu'snakt= science de mesure (mathématiques), tu'ssna n we'ktay).

