=== Ti'meslayin tu'snikin (''language mathématique'') ===
Tusnakt tesseqdac ta mslayt ig llan inettat d ta zedgant, uma yella tewwi'd kra n w'awalen aem [[aggay]] (groupe), [[ti ndert]] (anneau), d acu nbeddel asen anamek nsen i w'akken ad begnen i wetta usniken (termes mathématiques), akken daɣen ig lla w'assar nneɣ(notre besoin) i w'akken ad nessenfali(exprimer) kra n te ɣawsiwin, nesmentil'd (nesnulfay) awalen iɣ iwulmen aem [[ddutugdit]] (injection), [[nnigtugdit]] (surjection) neɣ [[allustugdit]] (bejsction), tugett n w'awalen usniken rran tusnakt d ta germant (difficile) i wid ur nessin tusnakt.

